title: HOUR 3- Reggie Miller Aug 25, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Reggie Miller Aug 25, 2020
description:
Reggie Miller says to Dan that the Lakers are a much different team when they are moving and passing the ball around. Reggie calls Luka Doncic shot against the Clippers a bad shot but says he has taken a many of those bad shots himself and made them too.
